{
    "type": "script",
    "id": "47132392-797d-4b95-8161-8d8003ae84d5",
    "name": "Magic Class Nights of the Dead",
    "sceneId": "981d126b-abc7-430a-abb4-e912340c59e6",
    "trigger": {
        "type": "triggers.manual",
        "name": "Manual"
    },
    "entryPoints": [
        {
            "type": "scripts.entryPoint",
            "id": "6fdc8e54-929a-4da5-aa6d-994b25f839e6",
            "name": "Main",
            "nodes": [
                {
                    "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                    "id": "532fbdd3-8909-4b96-832a-452bf90f177c",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "amount": "3",
                    "change": "1",
                    "notify": true
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "f0cf25ca-97f8-4765-b226-c55b325c25b8",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "Tonight will be the first of the Nights of the Dead celebration. This is a time when the gates that separate the lands of the living and that of the dead are opened and Spirits can cross over to this world.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "b193dca6-9dbf-424e-9db7-422b32f0a521",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "Of course, not every deceased soul chooses to return. Our world would be quite overrun with the dead if that were so. ",
                    "emotion": "1",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "8d60184c-67d3-49ea-ad9b-609266a64730",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "No, the ones who return are the strongest Willed individuals who have an unfilled need they did not achieve in life. Some return to say farewell to their loved ones... Others return to avenge the wrongs done to them in life.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "9b32a8ca-1185-441c-b62c-58dd3e22e677",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "Any ghosts you might meet within the castle will be benevolent ones. Nevertheless, you should avoid them whenever possible. All ghosts drain life energy in order to manifest themselves in this world.",
                    "emotion": "1",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "e25dc365-8f12-4bac-8d08-fc97bb2335b4",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "Does anyone have any questions about this?",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.showMenu",
                    "id": "9a878f67-6209-419c-bc72-682ef5bb1409",
                    "options": [
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "f0989499-da88-4365-a47a-eb684d8a56ce",
                            "text": "Ask About Talking to Ghosts",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "4e4ad54e-cf5f-4a37-9b88-27c8aea0b658",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "text": "Is there some way to talk to ghosts? I mean, are their moans meaningful?",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "be024c0c-9530-4a31-a89e-79d0036d766a",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "Some people like the Rovers can naturally communicate with the spirits of the dead. There are magic items and complex spells that can help one do so for those without such a gift.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "15cdd896-e351-4aa7-b7f6-5bae822114b4",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "However, such charms are beyond the purview of this class. Besides, it is very dangerous to approach the non-corporeal Undead. They all drain life to some degree or another.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "id": "fac87275-2d28-4230-a155-30a374b453fa",
                                    "type": "nodes.skillBranch",
                                    "skill": "Smarts",
                                    "target": "72",
                                    "success": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "failure": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "notify": true
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                    "id": "bc98ab77-0d1d-4458-a3ba-aaf24f5d0dc5",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "amount": "2",
                                    "change": "1",
                                    "notify": true
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "5",
                            "ExitMenu": false
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "301f1196-8418-4dc8-921b-8ba3ea780ccb",
                            "text": "Ask About Dealing with Ghosts",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "9794a8eb-cd89-493e-9b60-8c885a8a1c84",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "text": "Is it true that people can help ghosts rest in peace by helping them fulfill the goal that makes them restless?",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "4",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "a41b26f5-b2d0-41e2-b36e-ba160c97b286",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "Yes, it is possible to set a spirit to rest by helping them with their goal. Unfortunately, it's hard to tell a Ghost's goal unless you can speak with them.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "29c110f2-1758-4ce0-8e95-c4ab5153e46d",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "I have spells that will allow one to speak to Ghosts, but they do not last very long. If you truly wish to speak with Ghosts, you might speak with Chef Ifetaya. She seems to be quite knowledgeable about such things.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "4",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "id": "f914c517-07dd-475c-8ff1-e9519914a201",
                                    "type": "nodes.skillBranch",
                                    "skill": "Charm",
                                    "target": "72",
                                    "success": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "failure": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "notify": true
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                    "id": "f26b9c3d-a00d-49a8-8ae6-bdb92c28f313",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "amount": "2",
                                    "change": "1",
                                    "notify": true
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "6",
                            "ExitMenu": true
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "e34400fa-fe43-428d-851d-c9ec684e1b93",
                            "text": "Make a Joke",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "3e1202d3-1b97-4d8a-9a18-48cde40266df",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "text": "What happened when a boy ghost meets a girl ghost? - It's love at first Fright!",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "4",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "ee79fb8d-616b-4790-ba17-191f33e779d4",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "Let us get back to the topic at hand, please.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
